title: I NEED A CREW! - Holdfast: Nations at War
description:
Hey, guys, this is an announcement about my crew that I am setting up for Holdfast: Nations at war. If you are interested, join the stream group down below. Also, remember that we will have our first meeting on the 16th of September at 2 PM EST. I will give out the TS link in the steam group once I get it fixed :D

Steam group - http://steamcommunity.com/groups/mariecrew

JOIN MY DISCORD SERVER: https://discord.gg/JjR7UR3

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
